default3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAntimicrobial resistance has been of growing concern to RCUK for the past few years and we are encouraged that the profile has been raised at the highest levels.  
defaultWe welcome the opportunity to provide evidence to the Committee and have focuse
defaultd on those questions that fall within our combined remit and expertise.
