default20.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThere is 
defaulta broad 
defaultrecognition that the purely genomic approach used by some pharma
defaultceutical companies
default to identify new targets over the past 10 years has not yielded results.  
defaultThe research councils consider that a
default more holistic approach is needed to better understand cellular mechanisms, identify putative targets through genomics but couple this with whole-cell based assays and better animal models. 
